Good web hosts (preferably free)? Post a reply
19 posts	• Page 1 of 2 • 1, 2	Good web hosts (preferably free)?
by Jake-X on Fri Dec 17, 2010 8:59 pm	([msg=50621]see Good web hosts (preferably free)?[/msg])
I'd like recommendations for good hosts that will give me complete control over the design of my site (problem with Free Webs, Yola, Wix, etc. is that you have to use their site-builders). It would also be nice if they're free or at least low-cost. I just want to make a site so I can keep practicing my HTML skills so I don't get rusty.
