by insomaniacal on Fri Dec 17, 2010 10:14 pm	([msg=50631]see Re: Good web hosts (preferably free)?[/msg])
I used 110mb for a dump page before, and they seemed fairly reasonable. They add some scripts to your pages that display their ads, but in my brief experience it was good.http://www.solidwebhost.com also allows for FTP access, and they allow you to create 2 mysql databases as well, something which 110mb makes you pay for I think.
